    "two_phases": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Two Phases",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"antiacne-phases\">\n  <div class=\"antiacne-section-header\">\n    <span class=\"antiacne-label\">The Science</span>\n    <h2>Two Phases. One Complete Cure.</h2>\n    <p>Each phase is carefully formulated to target different aspects of acne treatment.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"antiacne-phases-grid\">\n    <div class=\"antiacne-phase antiacne-phase-1\">\n      <div class=\"antiacne-phase-badge\">Phase I — Days 1–15</div>\n      <h3>Deep Clean & Calm</h3>\n      <p>Intensively cleanses, fights bacteria, and reduces redness and inflammation.</p>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-ingredients-list\">\n        <h4>Key Ingredients</h4>\n        <div class=\"antiacne-ingredient-tags\">\n          <span>Hydrolyzed Collagen</span>\n          <span>Azelaic Acid</span>\n          <span>Niacinamide</span>\n          <span>Tea Tree Oil</span>\n          <span>Zinc Ferment</span>\n          <span>Glycerin</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"antiacne-phase antiacne-phase-2\">\n      <div class=\"antiacne-phase-badge\">Phase II — Days 16–30</div>\n      <h3>Balance & Regenerate</h3>\n      <p>Restores skin's natural equilibrium, promotes regeneration, and maintains clarity.</p>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-ingredients-list\">\n        <h4>Key Ingredients</h4>\n        <div class=\"antiacne-ingredient-tags\">\n          <span>Hydrolyzed Collagen</span>\n          <span>Azelaic Acid</span>\n          <span>Star Anise Extract</span>\n          <span>Dragon Fruit Extract</span>\n          <span>Red Clover Extract</span>\n          <span>Niacinamide</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "padding-block-start": 80,
        "padding-block-end": 80
      }
    },
    "testimonials": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Testimonials",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"antiacne-testimonials\">\n  <div class=\"antiacne-section-header\">\n    <span class=\"antiacne-label\">Real Results</span>\n    <h2>What Our Customers Say</h2>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"antiacne-reviews-grid\">\n    <div class=\"antiacne-review\">\n      <div class=\"antiacne-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n      <p>\"This product is amazing — it does exactly what it promises. My skin is beautiful, glowing, and acne has significantly reduced. I'll definitely keep buying it!\"</p>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer-info\">\n        <img class=\"antiacne-review-avatar\" src=\"{{ 'customer-1.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Nikola T.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer\"><strong>Nikola T.</strong></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"antiacne-review\">\n      <div class=\"antiacne-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n      <p>\"After trying these wipes, I'm genuinely surprised. My skin has improved, it's smoother, and acne has become minimal. I'd absolutely buy this again.\"</p>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer-info\">\n        <img class=\"antiacne-review-avatar\" src=\"{{ 'customer-2.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Vendula L.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer\"><strong>Vendula L.</strong></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"antiacne-review\">\n      <div class=\"antiacne-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n      <p>\"After the first use, you can already see results. The product significantly reduces redness. After a few days, acne improves dramatically.\"</p>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer-info\">\n        <img class=\"antiacne-review-avatar\" src=\"{{ 'customer-3.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Kristýna V.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer\"><strong>Kristýna V.</strong></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"antiacne-review\">\n      <div class=\"antiacne-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n      <p>\"I'm 25 and still have acne-prone skin. Thanks to AntiAcne, my painful subcutaneous acne barely forms anymore. My pores are visibly smaller and my skin feels absolutely perfect.\"</p>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer-info\">\n        <img class=\"antiacne-review-avatar\" src=\"{{ 'customer-4.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Lucie M.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer\"><strong>Lucie M.</strong></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"antiacne-review\">\n      <div class=\"antiacne-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n      <p>\"I've been treating acne for years and tried so many products. AntiAcne is one that actually works! I noticed changes after just one week. After a month, my skin is brighter, more even, and my pores are reduced.\"</p>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer-info\">\n        <img class=\"antiacne-review-avatar\" src=\"{{ 'customer-5.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Eliška F.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer\"><strong>Eliška F.</strong></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"antiacne-review\">\n      <div class=\"antiacne-stars\">★★★★☆</div>\n      <p>\"The packaging is stylish and portable — I even took it camping! My skin is less red and acne is significantly less visible. I'd recommend it for acne-prone skin and blackheads.\"</p>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer-info\">\n        <img class=\"antiacne-review-avatar\" src=\"{{ 'customer-6.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Nikol H.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <div class=\"antiacne-reviewer\"><strong>Nikol H.</strong></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-4",
        "section_width": "page-width",
