    "faq_section": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "FAQ",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"antiacne-faq\">\n  <div class=\"antiacne-section-header\">\n    <span class=\"antiacne-label\">Got Questions?</span>\n    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"antiacne-faq-list\">\n    <details class=\"antiacne-faq-item\">\n      <summary>What if my skin feels dry after using AntiAcne?</summary>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-faq-answer\"><p>AntiAcne wipes contain active ingredients that intensively cleanse and nourish skin in one step, fully replacing a regular skincare routine. However, every skin reacts differently. If you experience mild dryness, you can apply your favorite moisturizer after use. It won't reduce AntiAcne's effectiveness.</p></div>\n    </details>\n    <details class=\"antiacne-faq-item\">\n      <summary>How much water should I use to activate the wipe?</summary>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-faq-answer\"><p>Remove the protective paper and spray about 5–10 pumps of water onto the white nanofiber layer. Don't be afraid to use enough water — the better the nanofiber is moistened, the more effectively it works.</p></div>\n    </details>\n    <details class=\"antiacne-faq-item\">\n      <summary>Is AntiAcne suitable for sensitive skin?</summary>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-faq-answer\"><p>Yes. AntiAcne contains only natural active ingredients without preservatives or fragrances. Thanks to DrySerum technology, ingredients are released gradually and precisely, working gently yet effectively. If you have extremely sensitive skin, we recommend starting with a patch test.</p></div>\n    </details>\n    <details class=\"antiacne-faq-item\">\n      <summary>Can acne get worse during the treatment?</summary>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-faq-answer\"><p>For some people, acne may briefly become more visible in the first days. This is a natural skin purging process — active ingredients draw impurities to the surface. It's typically a temporary phase, followed by calming, balancing, and long-term improvement.</p></div>\n    </details>\n    <details class=\"antiacne-faq-item\">\n      <summary>Why is it important to complete the full 30-day treatment?</summary>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-faq-answer\"><p>AntiAcne is designed as a complete 30-day cure with two connected phases. Phase I knocks out acne — cleansing and reducing redness. Phase II restores balance, supports regeneration, and keeps skin calm. The best results come from completing both phases, as their combination delivers long-term effects.</p></div>\n    </details>\n    <details class=\"antiacne-faq-item\">\n      <summary>Why should I keep the tin box closed?</summary>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-faq-answer\"><p>The wipes are stored in a practical metal tin that protects their effectiveness throughout the 30-day cure. Water activates the active ingredients, so it's important to keep the box sealed and away from humidity. This ensures the ingredients only activate when you moisten and apply them to your skin.</p></div>\n    </details>\n    <details class=\"antiacne-faq-item\">\n      <summary>What is the \"InYourSkin\" project?</summary>\n      <div class=\"antiacne-faq-answer\"><p>\"InYourSkin\" is a joint project between AntiAcne and the nonprofit organization Srdcem Robinson. Its goal is to support not only healthy, confident skin but also families going through difficult situations. A portion of every AntiAcne purchase goes directly to supporting this cause.</p></div>\n    </details>\n  </div>\n</section>",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-3",
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "padding-block-start": 80,
        "padding-block-end": 80
      }
